<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Không tìm thấy trang</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;700&display=swap');

        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: #f2f4f8;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 120px;
            margin: 0;
            color: #0078D7;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin: 20px 0 10px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00bfff, #0078D7);
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #0078D7, #005EA6);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 80px;
            }
            h2 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            p {
                font-size: 16px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>404</h1>
        <h2>Không tìm thấy trang</h2>
        <p>Rất tiếc, trang bạn đang tìm kiếm không tồn tại hoặc đã bị xóa.</p>
        <a class="btn" href="/">Quay về trang chủ</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
